{
  "texts": [
    "This is no difference for adult learning and we shall choose the data-lite strategies.",
    "We first adopt pre-trained LLMs with optimal performance for understanding generic text content.",
    "Each LLM consists of many parameters and the optimal values for generic usage are known and downloadable for these LLMs.",
    "We take such optimal values as the starting point for customizing the parameters to adult learning.",
    "We adjust and optimize the values as a model re-training or fine-tuning process, and our ultimate goal is to adopt the parameter values for general-purpose text analysis to the domain of adult learning."
  ]
}